  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q60",
  "body": "How is the sabbath to be sanctified?\n\nThe sabbath is to be sanctified by a holy resting all that day, even from such worldly employments and recreations as are lawful on other days; and spending the whole time in the public and private exercises of God's worship, except so much as is to be taken up in the works of necessity and mercy.",
